Context:
The current handleBgOpenPluginTab (background-message-handlers.ts:612-648) has this fallback chain:
1. Find matching tabs → focus one (cycle through)
2. If no tabs, check meta.homepage → open it
3. If no homepage → return { opened: false }

We add step 2.5: check last-seen URL.

