```
Note: `tab` here is from `findAllMatchingTabs` which returns `chrome.tabs.Tab[]` — the `.url` field is available.

4. In background.ts (or wherever `loadLastKnownStateFromSession` is called during init/wake), also call `loadLastSeenUrlsFromStorage()`. Search for `loadLastKnownStateFromSession` in background.ts to find the exact location.

